In this I downloaded a llm model from ollama.
How to download a model: 
go to 'https://ollama.com/download' and download the ollama to the oporation system you have
after that got to the Models on the top right corner and look for a model you wold like
in this projects i used the 'phi3' model.
after that open a command prompt and run this command "ollama pull {your-model}"
it will download the llm you choose the run "ollama run {your-model}"
then it will start your llm you can 